ct):\n  time_seg = time() / 60\n  for secret in acct.get_secrets():\n    for offset in range(time_seg - 1, time_seg  + 2):  # 時間差\n      if hash(secret, offset) == code:\n        return True\n  return False</code></pre><br />\n<br />\n好似係"}]}